{
  "name": "MiniSwift",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "swift_versions": "5.0",
  "summary": "A minimal Flux-Redux architecture designed for Swift applications.",
  "description": "A minimal Flux-Redux architecture designed for Swift applications.\n\n  Mini is built to make Swift a first class citizen in Redux-Flux architecture for macOS, iOS and tvOS.\n  With Mini, you can create a thread-safe application with a predictable unidirectional data flow,\n  focusing on what really matters: build awesome applications.",
